https://jenkins.io/doc/　－＞　https://jenkins.io/doc/book/installing/

安装方法一：
    WAR file 

    １．安装前准备
        Java 8 (either a JRE or Java Development Kit (JDK) is fine)

        Docker

    ２．下载：http://mirrors.jenkins.io/war-stable/latest/jenkins.war

    ３．执行命令
        java -jar jenkins.war --httpPort=8080

    ４．浏览器打开http://localhost:8080

    ５．初始化密码的地方（用户名：admin）
        /home/eddychen3/.jenkins/secrets/initialAdminPassword

    ６．注意点：数据默认保存
      ＊＊＊保存在：/home/eddychen3/.jenkins目录下面＊＊＊
                  用户主目录

安装方法二：
    ｄｏｃｋｅｒ安装

    １．安装前准备
        Docker

    ２．下载镜像
        docker pull jenkinsci/blueocean

    ３．运行镜像 （＼后面不能有空格）
        sudo docker run \
          -u root \
          --rm \
          -d \
          -p 8080:8080 \
          -p 50000:50000 \
          -v jenkins-data:/var/jenkins_home \
          -v /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock \
          jenkinsci/blueocean

    ４．初始化密码存储目录
      /var/jenkins_home/secrets/initialAdminPassword

安装方法三：
    apt安装

    Java 8 (either a JRE or Java Development Kit (JDK) is fine)

    １．直接安装
        wget -q -O - https://pkg.jenkins.io/debian/jenkins.io.key | sudo apt-key add -
        sudo sh -c 'echo deb https://pkg.jenkins.io/debian-stable binary/ > /etc/apt/sources.list.d/jenkins.list'
        sudo apt-get update
        sudo apt-get install jenkins

    ２．可选：设置指定版本
        sudo apt-get install jenkins=2.138.1

        如果下载太慢
            先手动下载，再安装
            https://pkg.jenkins.io/debian/

    ３．查看日志
      /var/log/jenkins/jenkins.log

    问题及解决方案：
      问题１：
        install 的时候报错
          invoke-rc.d: initscript jenkins, action "start" failed.
          ● jenkins.service - LSB: Start Jenkins at boot time
             Loaded: loaded (/etc/init.d/jenkins; bad; vendor preset: enabled)
             Active: failed (Result: exit-code) since Fri 2019-04-26 16:38:53 CST; 6ms ago
               Docs: man:systemd-sysv-generator(8)
            Process: 32598 ExecStart=/etc/init.d/jenkins start (code=exited, status=1/FAILURE)

          Apr 26 16:38:53 172-20-53-204 systemd[1]: Starting LSB: Start Jenkins at boot time...
          Apr 26 16:38:53 172-20-53-204 jenkins[32598]: ERROR: No Java executable found in current PATH: /bin:/usr/bin:/sbin:/usr/sbin
          Apr 26 16:38:53 172-20-53-204 jenkins[32598]: If you actually have java installed on the system make sure the executable is in the aforementio...ble path
          Apr 26 16:38:53 172-20-53-204 systemd[1]: jenkins.service: Control process exited, code=exited status=1
          Apr 26 16:38:53 172-20-53-204 systemd[1]: Failed to start LSB: Start Jenkins at boot time.
          Apr 26 16:38:53 172-20-53-204 systemd[1]: jenkins.service: Unit entered failed state.
          Apr 26 16:38:53 172-20-53-204 systemd[1]: jenkins.service: Failed with result 'exit-code'.
          Hint: Some lines were ellipsized, use -l to show in full.
          dpkg: error processing package jenkins (--configure):
           subprocess installed post-installation script returned error exit status 1
          Errors were encountered while processing:
           jenkins
          E: Sub-process /usr/bin/dpkg returned an error code (1)
        解决方法：（https://blog.csdn.net/yi_suo_yan_yu/article/details/81981789）
          在/usr/bin下添加java可执行文件软连接

          ln -s /root/jdk/bin/java /usr/bin/java


＊＊＊推荐使用apt安装＊＊＊

  升级：
    sudo apt-get update
    sudo apt-get install jenkins


其他细节点：
  １．jenkins代码存储的工作空间路径(https://blog.csdn.net/ZZY1078689276/article/details/77485615)
    【系统管理】－＞【系统设置】－＞默认： /var/lib/jenkins

      /var/lib/jenkins/workspace
